All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AgeAndMaritalStatusEligibilityRule
A subclass of the abstract class EligibilityRule, this class checks for the age and marital status of an applicant
AgeOnlyEligibilityRule
A subclass of the abstract class EligibilityRule, this class only checks the age of applicants.
Applicant
Applicant is a subclass of User, but with added attributes specific to it to help facilitate the applicant role capabilities.
Application
Application class representing the data held by each Application object created by an applicant.
ApplicationController
Application Controller Class responsible for handling operations on application objects from different types of users.
ApplicationFilterService
Class for handling filtering of a list of applications
ApplicationStatus
 
ApplicationView
vApplication View Class responsible for displaying forms and information related to applications
AuthenticationService
Class for verification and search of user details
AuthView
AuthView class is responsible for displaying and collecting user input before login.
EligibilityRule
Abstract EligibilityRule class for determining the eligibility conditions for a specific flat type.
Enquiry
Enquiry class representing the data held in an enquiry object made by officers and applicants
EnquiryController
Enquiry Controller class for handling operations involving enquiries, such as creating, editing, replying and deleting
EnquiryView
Enquiry View class is responsible for displaying information and gathering user input for operations related to enquiries.
ExcelFileReader
Excel File Reader to take in and register user details from a csv file
FlatType
Flat type class representing the data held by each flat type object.
HDBManager
HDBManager class is a subclass of user, with added attributes to facilitate its unique capabilities.
HDBOfficer
HDB Officer class is a subclass of Applicant and has the same capabilities, but with additional officer-specific methods and attributes.
HDBOfficerController
HDB Officer Controller class responsible for operations related to HDB Officers.
IApplicationFilterService
An interface containing methods to filter lists of applications.
IApplicationService
Includes methods to modify and update application statuses, getting application statuses and requesting flat booking for applicant Implemented by application controllers
IAuthenticationService
Includes methods to check and search user details Implemented by Authentication classes for login functions
IEnquiryService
Interface for modifying enquiries.
IManagerService
Manager Interface for Officer Approval Implemented by HDBManagers, can be extended for other high level roles.
IOfficerService
Officer Service Interface including methods for officer registration Implemented by HDBOfficer Controller
IProjectService
Project service including methods related to project searching for managers.
IReportService
Report Service interface including methods to generate reports and receipts.
IUserService
User service interface including methods to login and change user profile details.
IWithdrawalService
Withdrawal Service interface including methods for modifying and retrieving withdrawal requests Implemented by WithdrawalController
Main
 
Project
Project class representing the data held by each project object.
ProjectController
Project Controller Class handling operations on projects
ProjectView
Project View class is responsible for displaying and gathering user input for operations related to projects.
Registration
Registration class represents the data held by each registration object.
RegistrationStatus
 
RegistrationView
Registration View class is responsible for displaying forms and information related to registrations.
Report
Report class responsible for printing information to the console as a report.
ReportController
Report Controller Class responsible for generating reports and receipts
ReportView
Report View class is responsible for printing manager and officer generated reports and receipts.
Role
 
Session
Session Class handles the tracking and granting of permissions to the current user during runtime.
SessionView
Session View class is responsible for showing the available actions a specific user is allowed to do after logging in.
User
User class is a superclass to all the different user roles: Applicant, HDBManager, HDBOfficer
UserController
User Controller Class responsible for handling generic User processes
UserRepository
This class is used only to extract information from csv files containing user details.
UserView
User View class is responsible for showing user information and forms regarding operations to modify user profile details
View
View interface showing default methods for use by all view classes.
WithdrawalController
Withdrawal controller class used for operations related to withdrawal requests.
WithdrawalRequest
WithdrawalRequest class represents the data held by withdrawal requests created by applicants who wish to withdraw their application.
WithdrawalRequestView
WithdrawalRequest View class is responsible for showing forms and displaying information relevant to withdrawal requests and their related operations.
